	<a href="http://glenhirshberg.com/site/booklist-waxes-enthusiastic-about-nothing-to-devour/" title="Permalink to Booklist waxes enthusiastic about NOTHING TO DEVOUR" rel="bookmark">
		<h1 class="title">Booklist waxes enthusiastic about NOTHING TO DEVOUR</h1>
	</a>

	&#8220;Hirshberg excels at slowly building an atmosphere of dread and foreboding, and&#8230;creating gritty, violent, and mesmerizing characters&#8230;&#8221; &#8212; Booklist (see&hellip;
